latestIgtvVideos.title: Sky divingg in Switzerland 🏔🪂
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Yesss it was the MOST adventurous thing i have everr done in my life. ❄️Trust mee when i say this, this should definitely be in your bucket list.💌 We were acting all cool and all until the day actually arrived.🙄 It was a mix of getting nervous and excited as hell at the samee time! Combination of snow covered as well as lush green mountains, most scenic clouds and the winds made the experience HEAVENLY!😭💙 The actual video was really long, so i’ve edited the parts I thought were the best. (where I didn’t look funny because of the wind blowing on my face😂)
.
P.S - I wishh to do a three day sky diving course and then dive alonee!💙
